1. Create clone of the project.
2. Eclipse -> New -> Import -> Existing Maven Project
3. Right click on the project and  Update Maven and run it locally. (eg: http://localhost:8081/rest-ws-deploy-heroku/myresource)
4. Cmd prompt-> go to your project path ->

heroku login
heroku create your-url
heroku open



URL for this project is : https://rest-ws-deploy-heroku.herokuapp.com/myresource

************************ If you want to create new project ************************

Group Id 		:    org.glassfish.jersey.archtype
Artifact Id 	:    jersey-heroku-webapp
Version 		:	 2.23.2